---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="max-w-screen-xl bg-gray-100 shadow-2xl mx-auto flex-1 text-slate-900">
		
		<!-- Header Section -->
		<section class="py-16" style="background-color: #9e383d;">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-4 victoria-font"
					style="font-family: 'Victoria', 'Times New Roman', serif;">
					About
				</h1>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-200">
					The story behind The Money-Printing Press and its mission to explore wealth through history.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Main Content -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-white">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
				
				<!-- About the Project -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8 text-slate-800 text-center victoria-font">
						The Money-Printing Press
					</h2>
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
						<div>
							<img
								src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6802042/pexels-photo-6802042.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
								alt="Historical money and wealth imagery"
								class="w-full h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-6">
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700">
								Welcome to The Money-Printing Press, a deep exploration of wealth creation, 
								preservation, and destruction throughout human history. This project examines 
								the timeless principles that have governed prosperity across cultures and centuries.
							</p>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700">
								From the merchant republics of medieval Italy to the financial innovations 
								of modern Silicon Valley, we trace the patterns and strategies that have 
								consistently created lasting wealth.
							</p>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700">
								By understanding these historical precedents, we can better navigate today's 
								financial landscape and build wealth that endures across generations.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- About Marcos -->
				<div class="mb-16 bg-gray-50 p-10 rounded-2xl">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8 text-slate-800 text-center victoria-font">
						About Marcos Vega
					</h2>
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="w-56 h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-300 to-gray-400 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
								<span class="text-gray-600 text-7xl">üì∏</span>
							</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 italic">
								Marcos Vega<br/>Financial Historian & Writer
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								Marcos Vega is a financial historian and wealth strategist with an insatiable curiosity 
								about the patterns that govern prosperity throughout history. With a background spanning 
								both quantitative finance and historical research, he brings a unique analytical lens 
								to the study of wealth creation.
							</p>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								His fascination began during graduate studies in economic history, where he discovered 
								that the same principles used by Venetian merchants in the 14th century were being 
								employed by modern venture capitalists. This revelation sparked a lifelong quest to 
								identify the timeless strategies that transcend specific eras and technologies.
							</p>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								When not researching historical financial documents or analyzing market patterns, 
								Marcos can be found exploring used bookstores for forgotten economic treatises, 
								traveling to historical financial centers, or crafting the perfect espresso‚Äîa skill 
								he argues is as essential as compound interest for long-term success.
							</p>
							<div class="border-l-4 pl-6 italic text-slate-600" style="border-left-color: #d4af37;">
								"The best investment strategies weren't invented yesterday‚Äîthey were perfected 
								centuries ago by people who understood that true wealth transcends any single 
								lifetime."
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Mission & Vision -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8 text-slate-800 text-center victoria-font">
						Mission & Philosophy
					</h2>
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
						<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border-l-4" style="border-left-color: #d4af37;">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4 victoria-font">Our Mission</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								To illuminate the timeless principles of wealth creation by examining 
								history's greatest fortunes and the strategies behind them. We believe 
								that understanding the past is key to building lasting prosperity in 
								the present‚Äîand that the most profound financial wisdom has already 
								been discovered, tested, and proven across multiple centuries.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border-l-4" style="border-left-color: #d4af37;">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4 victoria-font">Our Philosophy</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								True wealth creation follows patterns that have persisted for millennia. 
								By studying these patterns‚Äîfrom the trading strategies of ancient 
								Phoenicians to the investment principles of modern dynasties‚Äîwe can 
								build a comprehensive understanding that transcends market cycles, 
								technological disruptions, and economic upheavals.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- What You'll Find -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8 text-slate-800 text-center victoria-font">
						What You'll Discover Here
					</h2>
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
						<div class="text-center p-6">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg"
								 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9e383d, #7f1d1d);">
								<span class="text-white text-3xl">üìö</span>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3 victoria-font">Historical Case Studies</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								Deep dives into the strategies used by history's most successful wealth builders, 
								from the Medici banking empire to modern financial dynasties.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="text-center p-6">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg"
								 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9e383d, #7f1d1d);">
								<span class="text-white text-3xl">üîç</span>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3 victoria-font">Pattern Recognition</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								Analysis of recurring themes and strategies that appear across different 
								eras, cultures, and economic systems‚Äîthe true constants of wealth creation.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="text-center p-6">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg"
								 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9e383d, #7f1d1d);">
								<span class="text-white text-3xl">‚ö°</span>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3 victoria-font">Modern Applications</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
								Practical ways to apply historical insights to today's investment landscape, 
								business strategies, and personal wealth-building endeavors.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Personal Note -->
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-gray-100 p-10 rounded-2xl mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-6 text-center victoria-font">
						A Personal Note
					</h2>
					<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
						<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
							This project represents more than academic curiosity‚Äîit's a personal quest to understand 
							the fundamental forces that shape prosperity. Every article, every analysis, every historical 
							connection draws from years of research, countless conversations with experts, and a genuine 
							fascination with the stories behind great fortunes.
						</p>
						<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							My hope is that by sharing these discoveries, we can all become better stewards of wealth, 
							more thoughtful investors, and more informed participants in the great economic currents 
							that have shaped‚Äîand continue to shape‚Äîour world.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Contact -->
				<div class="text-center p-12 rounded-2xl" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9e383d, #7f1d1d);">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 victoria-font">
						Let's Connect
					</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
						Have questions about wealth through the ages? Discovered an interesting historical 
						financial pattern? Or simply want to discuss the intersection of history and finance? 
						I'd love to hear from you.
					</p>
					<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
						<a
							href="mailto:marcos@moneyprinting.press"
							class="inline-block bg-white text-slate-800 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition shadow-lg"
						>
							Email Marcos
						</a>
						<a
							href="/archive"
							class="inline-block border-2 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg"
							style="border-color: #d4af37; color: #d4af37;"
							onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#d4af37'; this.style.color='#9e383d';"
							onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#d4af37';"
						>
							Explore the Archive
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.victoria-font {
		font-family: 'Victoria', 'Times New Roman', serif;
	}
</style>